					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Hi, I have a short question: is it correct that by continuously polling $2002 in a very tight loop, it may happen that NMI's won't occur? Because that's exactly how Nintendulator and Nestopia behave, but not FCE Ultra.
<br />
<br />I'd just like to have a confirmation that this illogical and stupid behaviour also happens on the real hardware. Thanks!</div>

